    40002 [label="LicenseTag (ScopedLicenseTag \"OrtLicenseCategorization\" \"include-in-notice-file\" (LicenseTagDescription \"Same as above, as a temporary work-around for the category name not being configurable in ORT reports, see https://github.com/oss-review-toolkit/ort/issues/8220.\"))"
